components.name: SelectComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field appearance="outline">
  <mat-label>Label</mat-label>
  <mat-select *ngIf="isMultiple" multiple
              (selectionChange)="onSelectionChange($event)"
              [formControl]="selectControl"
              disableOptionCentering
              panelClass="select-margin-top">

    <mat-option value="" *ngIf="defaultOption">
      {{defaultOption}}
    </mat-option>

    <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options"
                [value]="option"  
                (click)="onClick()">
      {{option.desc}}
    </mat-option>
  </mat-select>

  <mat-select *ngIf="!isMultiple"
              (selectionChange)="onSelectionChange($event)"
              [formControl]="selectControl"
              disableOptionCentering
              panelClass="select-margin-top">

    <mat-option value="" *ngIf="defaultOption">
      {{defaultOption}}
    </mat-option>

    <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options"
                [value]="option"  
                (click)="onClick()">
      {{option.desc}}
    </mat-option>
  </mat-select>

</mat-form-field>
